<bibRefCitation id="1F7D4B5A6E32FFC44635E7E18406FB44" author="Balsamo, M. &amp; d'Hondt, J. L. &amp; Kisielewski, J. &amp; Pierboni, L." box="[863,1104,1242,1268]" pageId="3" pageNumber="352" pagination="85 - 91" refId="ref3591" refString="Balsamo, M., d'Hondt, J. L., Kisielewski, J., Pierboni, L. 2008. Global diversity of gastrotrichs (Gastrotricha) in fresh waters. Hydrobiologia, 595, 85 - 91." type="journal article" year="2008">Balsamo et al., 2008</bibRefCitation>
). Reported from Europe: 
<collectingCountry id="03FB763B6E32FFC4443EE7C18191FAA4" box="[340,455,1274,1300]" name="Denmark" pageId="3" pageNumber="352">Denmark</collectingCountry>
